==English==

===Etymology===
From Greek [[ξένος]] (''xénos'', foreign) + [[φόβος]] (''phobos'', fear) + [[-ia]].

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊbiə|-əʊbiə]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# pathological fear of [[foreigner|foreigners]].
# pathological hatred for [[foreigner|foreigners]].
# pathological fear/hatred of the unknown.

====Related terms====
*[[xenophobe]]
*[[xenophobic]]

